  "page": "Brynden (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The name <b>Brynden</b> can refer to the following characters:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Blackwood\" title=\"Brynden Blackwood\">Brynden Blackwood</a>, the eldest son and heir of Lord Tytos Blackwood of Raventree Hall</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a>, also known as <i>Bloodraven</i>, the bastard son of King Aegon IV Targaryen and Lady Melissa Blackwood</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Tully\" title=\"Brynden Tully\">Brynden Tully</a>, also known as the <i>Blackfish</i>, the younger brother of Lord Hoster Tully</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_Also\">See Also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brynden_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See Also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bryndon_Hightower\" title=\"Bryndon Hightower\">Bryndon Hightower</a>, a cousin of Lord Ormund Hightower, killed during the Dance of the Dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Brandon (disambiguation)\">Brandon (disambiguation)</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403221432\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache wi